name: 2024 The 11th International Conference on Artificial Intelligence
content: Publication: Paper accepted by ICOAI 2024 will be published in Journal of Advances in Information Technology (JAIT, https://www.jait.us/, ISSN: 1798-2340 (Online)) Abstracting/Indexing: ESCI (Web of Science), Scopus, EBSCO, Google Scholar, CNKI, etc. Or International Journal of Machine Learning (IJML, http://ijml.org/, ISSN: 2972-368X) Abstracting/Indexing: Inspec (IET), Google Scholar, Crossref, ProQuest, Electronic Journals Library, CNKI.
